data.description: Step into this affordable opportunity of home ownership.  This townhouse is move in ready, freshly painted, new carpeting and laminate flooring, LG Smart appliances, A/C one year old and newer hot water heater. Thomasville kitchen cabinetry, 3 new ceiling fans. Complete package of home furnishings with accepted full offer. The townhouse is located within steps of the crystal clear pool and spa for your enjoyment and relaxation. Conveniently located to GCC, GCU and ASU West. Take a tour today, you won't be disappointed.
